Stack: JavaScript, HTML/CSS, Node.js, Vercel, Supabase, GitHub
Key architecture: Progressive Web Application with cloud and local models
Mobius_Coder is forked from Mobius_Vercel and uses a stripped-down version of its codebase
It utilises a Supabase project with a schema containing five tables for data storage
The application has a GitHub repository and a Vercel project for deployment

